In [75]:
def extract_spectrograms(path):
    os.chdir(path)

    spectrograms = []

    with os.scandir(path) as files:
        for file in files:
            #print(file.name)
            if file.name.endswith('.png'):
                spectrograms.append(file.path)
        return spectrograms

def createFolder(directory):
    try:
        if not os.path.exists(directory):
            os.makedirs(directory)
    except OSError:
        print ('Error: Creating directory. ' +  directory)

In [38]:
def fill_df_with_label(spectrograms, label):
    new_df =  pd.DataFrame()
    new_df['filename'] = spectrograms
    new_df['label'] = [label] * len(spectrograms)
    return new_df
In [45]:
def make_dataset(train_ushape, train_noushape):
    tuf0 = train_ushape[:33]
    tuf1 = train_ushape[33:66]
    tuf2 = train_ushape[66:99]
    tuf3 = train_ushape[99:133]
    tuf4 = train_ushape[133:]
    
    tnf0 = train_noushape[:78]
    tnf1 =train_noushape[78:156]
    tnf2 =train_noushape[156:234]
    tnf3 =train_noushape[234:312]
    tnf4 =train_noushape[312:392]
    
    df_train_0 = pd.concat([fill_df_with_label(tuf0, "ushape"),fill_df_with_label(tnf0, "noushape")])
    df_train_1 = pd.concat([fill_df_with_label(tuf1, "ushape"),fill_df_with_label(tnf1, "noushape")])
    df_train_2 = pd.concat([fill_df_with_label(tuf2, "ushape"),fill_df_with_label(tnf2, "noushape")])
    df_train_3 = pd.concat([fill_df_with_label(tuf3, "ushape"),fill_df_with_label(tnf3, "noushape")])
    df_train_4 = pd.concat([fill_df_with_label(tuf4, "ushape"),fill_df_with_label(tnf4, "noushape")])
    
    return df_train_0, df_train_1, df_train_2, df_train_3, df_train_4
In [40]:
def create_model(METRICS):
  model = Sequential([
    #data_augmentation,
    layers.Input(shape=(224, 224, 3)),
    layers.Rescaling(1./255),
    layers.Conv2D(16, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),
    layers.MaxPooling2D(),
    layers.Conv2D(32, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),
    layers.MaxPooling2D(),
    layers.Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),
    layers.MaxPooling2D(),
    layers.Dropout(0.2),
    layers.Flatten(),
    layers.Dense(128, activation='relu'),
    layers.Dense(1, activation='sigmoid')
  ])
  model.compile(optimizer='SGD',
                loss='binary_crossentropy',
                metrics=METRICS)
  return model
In [41]:
METRICS = [
      keras.metrics.BinaryAccuracy(name='accuracy'),
      keras.metrics.Precision(name='precision'),
      keras.metrics.Recall(name='recall'),
      keras.metrics.AUC(name='auc'),
      keras.metrics.AUC(name='prc', curve='PR'), # precision-recall curve
]

In [43]:
def cross_val_5(df_0, df_1, df_2, df_3, df_4):
    train_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(
            featurewise_center=True,
            featurewise_std_normalization=True,
            rotation_range=20,
            width_shift_range=0.2,
            height_shift_range=0.2,
            horizontal_flip=True,
        )      
        
    valid_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(
            featurewise_center=True,
            featurewise_std_normalization=True,
            rotation_range=20,
            width_shift_range=0.2,
            height_shift_range=0.2,
            horizontal_flip=True,
        ) 
    df = pd.concat([df_0, df_1, df_2, df_3, df_4])
    for i in range(5):
        df_1 = df[i*111:i*111+111]
        df_2 = df[:i*111]
        df_2 = pd.concat([df_2,df[i*111+111:]])
        train(df_1, df_2)
        
    return 0

            featurewise_std_normalization=True,
            rotation_range=20,
            width_shift_range=0.2,
            height_shift_range=0.2,
            horizontal_flip=True,
        )      
        
valid_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(
            featurewise_center=True,
            featurewise_std_normalization=True,
            rotation_range=20,
            width_shift_range=0.2,
            height_shift_range=0.2,
            horizontal_flip=True,
        )
In [128]:
def train(df_train, df_val):
    train_generator = train_datagen.flow_from_dataframe(
        df_train,
        x_col='filename',
        y_col='label',
        class_mode='binary',
        target_size=(224, 224),
    )

    valid_generator = valid_datagen.flow_from_dataframe(
        df_val,
        x_col='filename',
        y_col='label',
        class_mode='binary',
        target_size=(224, 224),
    )
    
    epochs = 20
    model = create_model(METRICS)
    history = model.fit_generator(generator=
      train_generator,
      validation_data = valid_generator,
      epochs=epochs,
    )
    
    val_acc = history.history['val_accuracy']
    return val_acc[19] # 마지막 정확도 값
In [129]:
def cross_val_5(train_ushape, train_noushape):
    df_0, df_1, df_2, df_3, df_4 = make_dataset(train_ushape, train_noushape)
    df = pd.concat([df_0, df_1, df_2, df_3, df_4])
    avr = 0
    for i in range(5):
        print("\n\n=======================================================================\n\n")
        print( f"local times:{i}")
        print("\n\n=======================================================================\n\n")
        df_1 = df[i*111:i*111+111]
        df_2 = df[:i*111]
        df_2 = pd.concat([df_2,df[i*111+111:]])
        acc = train(df_1, df_2)
        avr = acc+avr
    avr = avr/5
    return avr

list_avr = []
for i in range(200):
    print("\n\n\n=======================================================================\n\n\n")
    print( f"Times:{i}")
    print("\n\n\n=======================================================================\n\n\n")
    sample_noushape = random.sample(train_noushape, 392)
    average = cross_val_5(train_ushape, sample_noushape)
    print(f"\n\n\n=========================={i} end =============================================\n\n\n")
    print(f"average:{average}")
    list_avr.append(average)
